                     <interp inst="t18250915-93-person565" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am a constable. On the 11th of August, I apprehended the prisoner - I stated the charge to him; he said nothing to it.</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. When I got into Chiswell-street, I lost the money, and was afraid to return.</p>

               <p>GEORGE THOMPSON. He never stated this before.</p>
